properties.name: activeSubscribers
properties.description: Number of currently active subscribers, meaning the ones with at least one client connected.
properties.rawdescription: Number of currently active subscribers, meaning the ones with at least one client connected.

properties.name: backlogSize
properties.description: Size of the messages backlog in bytes.
properties.rawdescription: Size of the messages backlog in bytes.

properties.name: backlogUsagePercentage
properties.description: Percentage of the backlog used. Value range is from o to 100. E.g. if 10% of the backlog is used, this value will be 10 (not 0.1).
properties.rawdescription:
Percentage of the backlog used. Value range is from o to 100.
E.g. if 10% of the backlog is used, this value will be 10 (not 0.1).

properties.name: msgRateIn
properties.description: Total rate of messages published on the topic (msg/s).
properties.rawdescription: Total rate of messages published on the topic (msg/s).

properties.name: msgRateOut
properties.description: Total rate of messages dispatched for the topic (msg/s).
properties.rawdescription: Total rate of messages dispatched for the topic (msg/s).

properties.name: namespace
properties.description: Namespace name that the topic belongs to.
properties.rawdescription: Namespace name that the topic belongs to.

properties.name: persistent
properties.description: If the topic is persistent or not. If false, the topic is not saved and will be deleted if there are no clients.
properties.rawdescription: If the topic is persistent or not. If false, the topic is not saved and will be deleted if there are no clients.

properties.name: subscribers
properties.description: Number of all subscribers for the topic.
properties.rawdescription: Number of all subscribers for the topic.

properties.name: unackMsgBacklog
properties.description: Number of unacknowledged messages in the backlog for topic for all subscribers.
properties.rawdescription: Number of unacknowledged messages in the backlog for topic for all subscribers.
